p: Data availability - XML files and datasets analysed in this study are available in the GitHub repository (https://github.com/CADDECentre/DENV2-PILOT). New sequences have been deposited in GenBank under accession numbers 959467 - 959485 [ Supplementary data (Table III)]. Raw sequence data have been deposited in SRA database from NCBI under numberPRJNA606238.
